=== 拍攝與後期製作 ===
第一次進行電影的試鏡時，[[羅伯·派汀森|羅伯·派汀森]]於哈德維克的家中床上親吻[[克莉絲汀·史都華|克莉絲汀·史都華]]。「那張床使派汀森成為了現在的他。」里德說。

這裡也是哈德維克為[[伊雯·瑞秋·伍德|伊雯·瑞秋·伍德]]試鏡的地方，她在床上跟[[妮琪·利德|妮琪·利德]]為電影《[[愛不回家|愛不回家]]》試演。當問及她的地方，哈德維克說：「[[音樂電視網|MTV]]來了，並在我家作為一集拍攝了那張床。這是個傳說<ref name="N"/>。」經過一個多星期的排練<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediablvd.com/magazine/the_news/celebrity/kellan_lutz_and_his_high_profile_projects_200808081250.html |title=Kellan Lutz And His High Profile Projects |author=Christina Radish |date=2008-08-08 |publisher=MediaBlvd Magazine |accessdate=2008-10-31 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915012946/http://www.mediablvd.com/magazine/the_news/celebrity/kellan_lutz_and_his_high_profile_projects_200808081250.html |archivedate=2008-09-15 }}</ref>，主要拍攝花了44天<ref name=reshoots>{{cite news |url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/08/twilight-re-sho.html |title='Twilight' reshoots: Why is Catherine Hardwicke filming again? |author=Nicole Sperling |date=2009-10-29 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Inc |accessdate=2008-10-13 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081019173635/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2008/08/twilight-re-sho.html |archivedate=2008-10-19 }}</ref>，並於2008年5月2日完成<ref name="filmingcomlete"/>。跟她的導演處女作《愛不回家》相似，哈德威克選擇廣泛使用手提攝影機來使電影具「真實感覺」<ref name=premierefacinelli>{{cite web |url=http://www.premiere.com/Feature/Exclusive-Interview-Peter-Facinelli-on-Twilight |title=Exclusive Interview: Peter Facinelli on 'Twilight' |author=Sona Charaipotra |work=Premiere.com |publisher=Hachette Filipacchi Media |accessdate=2010-08-12 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325085507/http://www.premiere.com/Feature/Exclusive-Interview-Peter-Facinelli-on-Twilight |archivedate=2010-03-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/movies/la-ca-twilight11-2008may11,0,5524758.story |title='Twilight' taps teen-vampire romance |author=Mike Russell |date=2008-05-11 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2008-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081019033815/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/movies/la-ca-twilight11-2008may11,0,5524758.story |archive-date=2008-10-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

梅爾曾三度參觀拍攝現場，並就故事的不同方面進行了諮詢<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.premiere.com/features/4673/the-twilight-phenomenon-the-director-and-author-at-comic-con-2008-page2.html |title=The 'Twilight' Phenomenon: The Director and Author at Comic-Con 2008 |author=Pamela Chelin |date=July 2008 |work=Premiere.com |publisher=Hachette Filipacchi Media |accessdate=2008-10-25 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025092121/http://www.premiere.com/features/4673/the-twilight-phenomenon-the-director-and-author-at-comic-con-2008-page2.html |archivedate=2008-10-25 }}</ref>；她在電影中也有一個簡短的客串<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1584977/story.jhtml |title='Twilight' Author Stephenie Meyer's Cameo: More Details Emerge From Book-Turned-Movie's Set |author=Larry Carroll |date=2008-04-08 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2008-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216021851/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1584977/story.jhtml |archive-date=2008-12-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

飾演吸血鬼的演員避免受陽光曝曬以保持皮膚的顏色蒼白，儘管化妝也可以達到這效果，並戴了隱形眼鏡。[[彼得·費辛利|彼得·費辛利]]解釋說：「我們之所以採用金色，是因為庫倫家族的人眼睛都是金色的。然後當我們飢餓的時候，我們必須戴上黑色的...<ref name=premierefacinelli/>」他們還跟舞蹈編舞員一起參加排練，觀察了不同的[[豹屬|豹的形態]]來使身體動作更優雅<ref name=premierefacinelli/><ref name=greene/><ref name=premieregigandet/>。

拍攝場景主要在[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|俄勒岡州波特蘭]]拍攝<ref name=reed>{{cite news | author=Larry Carroll | url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1581592/story.jhtml | title='Twilight' Finds Its Latest Victims: Nikki Reed, Rachelle Lefevre Added To Cast | publisher=MTV | date=2008-02-14 | accessdate=2008-02-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090919013825/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1581592/story.jhtml | archive-date=2009-09-19 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

特技工作主要由演員來完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=5257&Itemid=99 |title=It's TWILIGHT at Comic-Con! |author=Erin Cadwallader |date=2008-07-24 |publisher=IESB.net |accessdate=2008-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915110050/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=5257&Itemid=99 |archive-date=2008-09-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在拍攝的第一周於一個芭蕾舞工作室中拍攝派汀森和吉甘戴角色的戰鬥序列，由於故事中的吸血鬼具有超乎常人的力量與速度，因此涉及大量的「吊鋼絲」<ref name=premieregigandet>{{cite web |url=http://www.premiere.com/features/4674/twilights-bad-boy-vampire-cam-gigandet.html |title='Twilight's Bad Boy Vampire: Cam Gigandet |author=Pamela Chelin |work=Premiere.com |publisher=Hachette Filippachi Media |accessdate=2008-10-29 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004041755/http://www.premiere.com/features/4674/twilights-bad-boy-vampire-cam-gigandet.html |archivedate=2008-10-04 }}</ref>。

吉甘戴因此加入了[[綜合格鬥|綜合格鬥]]的戰鬥動作，並且以雞肉和蜂蜜代替鮮肉來維持身材<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1591709/20080729/story.jhtml |title='Twilight' Tuesday: 10 Things Comic-Con Taught Us About 'Twilight' |author=Larry Carroll |date=2008-07-29 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2008-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919213537/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1591709/20080729/story.jhtml |archive-date=2008-09-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

主角貝拉在這些事件中失去意識，並且由於這部小說是從她的角度講述，因此這些場景是電影中具說明性而且是獨特的<ref name=pattinsonlefevre/>。派汀森指出，在吊鋼絲時，保持重心是很困難的，「因為你必須真正與它抗爭並讓它做它需要做的事情<ref name=pattinsonlefevre/>。」瑞秋·拉菲佛（Rachelle Lefevre）發現她控制不了往前的動作，這感覺就好像沒有方向感了<ref name=pattinsonlefevre/>。

除了在{{le|福克斯高中|Forks High School}}本身拍攝外，學校的場景還在卡拉瑪高中<ref>{{cite news | author=Paige Dickerson | url=http://www.peninsuladailynews.com/article/20080310/NEWS/803100307 | title='Twilight' to film one or two days in LaPush | publisher=Peninsula Daily News | date=2008-03-09 | accessdate=2008-03-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715063949/http://www.peninsuladailynews.com/article/20080310/NEWS/803100307 | archive-date=2011-07-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>（Kalama High School）及{{le|麥迪遜高中|Madison High School (Portland, Oregon)}}拍攝<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/n/a/2008/04/15/entertainment/e113257D92.DTL |title=Teen vampire-love story `Twilight' being filmed in Oregon |author=Sarah Skidmore |date=2008-04-15 |work=San Francisco Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Communications |accessdate=2008-10-31 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216085844/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fn%2Fa%2F2008%2F04%2F15%2Fentertainment%2Fe113257D92.DTL |archivedate=2008-12-16 }}</ref>。

同年8月，其他場景在{{le|俄勒岡州聖海倫斯|St. Helens, Oregon}}<ref name=helens>{{cite news | author=Darryl Swan | url=http://www.spotlightnews.net/news/story.php?story_id=120716424131387500 | title='Twilight' descends on St. Helens | publisher=South Country Spotlight | date=2008-04-02 | accessdate=2008-05-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080505050441/http://www.spotlightnews.net/news/story.php?story_id=120716424131387500 | archive-date=2008-05-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，及哈德維克在[[帕薩迪納_(加利福尼亞州)|加利福尼亞州帕薩迪納]]進行了一些重拍工作<ref name=reshoots/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1593481/story.jhtml |title='Twilight' Cast Heads Back To The Set To Shoot New Scenes |author=Sabrina Rojas Weiss |date=2008-08-25 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2008-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913005418/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1593481/story.jhtml |archive-date=2008-09-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《暮光之城》原訂於2008年12月12日在美國上映，但由於《[[哈利波特：混血王子的背叛_(電影)|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛]]》改期於2009年7月上映，其後《暮光之城》改期於同年11月21日上映<ref name=thompson>{{cite news |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990652.html |title='Twilight' moves into 'Potter's' place |author=Anne Thompson |date=2008-08-15 |work=Variety |publisher=Reed Business Information |accessdate=2008-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204161251/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990652.html |archive-date=2008-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了宣傳電影而發布的兩輯預告片以及額外的一些場景，作為最終預告片於10月9日發布<ref>{{cite news |url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/918/918278p1.html |title=Twilight Trailer Tonight |author=Brian Linder |date=2008-10-09 |publisher=IGN Entertainment |accessdate=2008-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012174002/http://movies.ign.com/articles/918/918278p1.html |archive-date=2008-10-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1596753/20081009/story.jhtml |title=Final 'Twilight' Trailer, Shot By Shot: Romance, Violence ... And Prom! |author=Larry Carroll |date=2008-10-09 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2008-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013031724/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1596753/20081009/story.jhtml |archive-date=2008-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[意大利|意大利]]的[[羅馬影展|羅馬影展]]期間，展示了15分鐘的《暮光之城》的電影摘錄<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1596185/story.jhtml |title='Twilight' Sneak Peek To Premiere At International Rome Film Festival |author=Larry Carroll |date=2008-10-02 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2008-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004233216/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1596185/story.jhtml |archive-date=2008-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

電影因「有些暴力和色情場面」而被[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]評為[[美國電影分級制度#美國電影協會電影分級|PG-13]]的級別<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=7689 |title=MPAA Rating for Twilight |date=2008-09-10 |publisher=ShockTillYouDrop.com |accessdate=2008-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216085847/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=7689 |archive-date=2008-12-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

