== 發行 ==
=== 票房 ===
僅2008年11月21日午夜演出，《吸血新世紀》的票房收入已超過了$700萬美元<ref name=mcclintock>{{cite news | author=Pamela McClintock | title='Twilight' shining bright at box office | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117996294.html?categoryid=10&cs=1 | work=Variety | publisher=Reed Business Information | date=2008-11-21 | accessdate=2008-11-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090309070342/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117996294.html?categoryid=10&cs=1 | archive-date=2009-03-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影在[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]]整個時候的預售票房榜上排名第五，其前方包括翌年的[[吸血新世紀2：新月傳奇|續集]]、2005年的《[[星際大戰三部曲：西斯大帝的復仇|星球大戰前傳：黑帝君臨]]》、2008年的《[[黑暗騎士|蝙蝠俠—黑夜之神]]》及2009年的《[[哈利波特：混血王子的背叛_(電影)|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛]]》<ref name=mcclintock/>。開畫當天的票房收入為$3,570萬美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/days/?page=open&p.htm |title=Opening Day Records at the Box Office |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2008-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102013246/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/days/?page=open&p.htm |archive-date=2018-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美國和加拿大上映的第一個周末，《吸血新世紀》於3,419個影院累積了$6,960萬美元的票房，平均每個影院的收益為$20,368美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=twilight08.htm |title=Twilight (2008) Weekend Box Office Results |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2009-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091124144938/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=twilight08.htm |archive-date=2009-11-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於美國及加拿大的總票房收入為$192,769,854美元，國際的總票房為$199,846,771美元，合計總票房為$392,616,625美元<ref name=boxoffice/>。其上映周末總票房是所有女性導演的電影以來最高的，超越了1998年的《[[末日救未來|末日救未來]]》<ref>{{cite web|title='Twilight' Tuesday Finale: Director Catherine Hardwicke Raves About Film's Success — 'Unbelievable!'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600145/20081124/story.jhtml|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2010-07-10|author=Larry Carroll|date=2008-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100807064244/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1600145/20081124/story.jhtml|archive-date=2010-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《吸血新世紀》從影評人獲得褒貶不一的評價。根據《[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]網站》收集到的218個評論，該電影評分為49％，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]為5.41/10。該網站的關鍵共識寫道：「《吸血新世紀》在轉移到大銀幕時，已經失去了很多吸引力，它取悅其忠實的粉絲，但對門外漢卻無能為力<ref name=RT>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/ |title=Twilight (2008) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango Media]] |accessdate=2018-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091106215543/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/ |archive-date=2009-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」在《[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]》，基於電影評論家的37個評論，其[[加權平均數|平均得分]]為56分，表示「混合評論或平均評論」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/twilight |title=Twilight Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2018-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805110609/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/twilight |archive-date=2018-08-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《{{le|紐約新聞|New York Press}}》的評論家{{le|阿爾蒙德·懷特|Armond White}}稱這部電影為「真正的流行經典<ref>White, Armond (2008-11-21). [http://www.nypress.com/article-18961-twilight-bronte-never-dies.html "Twilight: Bronte Never Dies"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nypress.com/article-18961-twilight-bronte-never-dies.html |date=20081219230809 }}, ''[[New_York_Press|New York Press]]''. Retrieved on 2008-01-10.</ref>」，並讚揚哈德威克「把梅爾的小說系列轉變為[[勃朗特三姊妹|勃朗特三姊妹]]式的願景<ref>White, Armond (2008-01-07). [http://www.nypress.com/article-19237-better-than-list-2008.html "Better-Than List 2008"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nypress.com/article-19237-better-than-list-2008.html |date=20090218114318 }}, ''[[New_York_Press|New York Press]]''. Retrieved on 2008-01-10.</ref>」。[[罗杰·伊伯特|羅渣·伊拔]]在四顆星中給這部電影2.5顆星，並寫道：「我是在一個預告片上看到它的。上次我在同一個電影院看電影時，觀眾對此表示歡迎，因為這是個趕上八卦、發短訊、在個人笑話中取笑的機會。這次，觀眾全神貫注<ref>Ebert, Roger (2008-11-19). [http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081119/REVIEWS/811199997/1023 "Twilight"] {{Wayback|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20081119%2FREVIEWS%2F811199997%2F1023 |date=20120722195715 }}, ''[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]''. Retrieved on 2009-03-23.</ref>」。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的肯尼斯·圖蘭（Kenneth Turan）寫道：「《吸血新世紀》是不加掩飾的浪漫。除了故事本身固有的糊塗之外，它還旨在傳達與您一直在等待的一個特殊人物相遇的魔力。也許在畢竟幾個小時內有可能成為13歲和一個女性<ref>Turan, Kenneth (2008-11-21). [http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-et-twilight21-2008nov21,0,2377824.story "Twilight"], ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]''. Retrieved on 2009-03-23. {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220110140/http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-et-twilight21-2008nov21,0,2377824.story |date=2009-02-20 }}</ref>。」《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》給這部電影四分之二顆星，克勞迪婭·普伊格（Claudia Puig）寫道：「據說梅爾參與了《吸血新世紀》的製作，但她的小說遠比那無意間有趣且很快會被遺忘的電影更吸引<ref>Puig, Claudia (2008-11-20). [https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2008-11-19-twilight_N.htm?csp=IMDBreviews "Twilight"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2008-11-19-twilight_N.htm?csp=IMDBreviews |date=20111025091533 }}, ''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]''. Retrieved on 2009-03-23.</ref>。」《[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]》把電影評為「B級」，歐文·格里伯曼（Owen Gleiberman）讚揚哈德威克的執導方向：「她把梅爾的小說重新演繹成為充滿暴風雨的天空，蕩漾的荷爾蒙，和低估視覺效果的豪雨心情作品<ref>Gleiberman, Owen (2008-11-20). [http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20241357,00.html "Twilight"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20241357,00.html |date=20141024090339 }}, ''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''. Retrieved on 2009-03-23.</ref>。」

=== 家庭影院 ===
電影於2009年3月21日以通過午夜發布派對的形式在北美發行電影DVD，在推出的第一天就售出了超過300萬張<ref name="release">{{cite press release |title=Summit Home Entertainment's Saturday Release of Twilight Unleashes With Over 3 Million Units Sold |url=http://news.prnewswire.com/DisplayReleaseContent.aspx?ACCT=104&STORY=/www/story/03-22-2009/0004992497&EDATE= |publisher=[[Summit_Entertainment|Summit Entertainment]] |date=2009-03-22 |accessdate=2009-03-22 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326032320/http://news.prnewswire.com/DisplayReleaseContent.aspx?ACCT=104&STORY=%2Fwww%2Fstory%2F03-22-2009%2F0004992497&EDATE= |archivedate=2009-03-26 }}</ref>。它於2009年4月6日在英國發布<ref>{{cite news | title=''Twilight'' DVD Date, Art | url=http://shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=9110 | publisher=Shock Till You Drop | date=2009-01-07 | accessdate=2009-01-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090116021430/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=9110 | archive-date=2009-01-16 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B001O0DM2S |title=Twilight - 2 Disc Special Edition |publisher=Amazon.co.uk |accessdate=2010-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107000549/http://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B001O0DM2S |archive-date=2015-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。額外功能包括大約10至12個擴展或刪除的場景、蒙太奇和音樂特輯、幕後訪談，「製作」特輯，以及哈德維克、史都華和派汀森的訪問<ref>{{cite news | author=Larry Carroll | title='Twilight' Director Catherine Hardwicke Reveals DVD Details | url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1601060/story.jhtml | publisher=MTV | date=2008-12-11 | accessdate=2009-01-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090116073812/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1601060/story.jhtml | archive-date=2009-01-16 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author=Larry Carroll | title='Twilight' Director Catherine Hardwicke Talks About Edward And Bella's Chemistry, Potential Sequels | url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1599140/20081111/story.jhtml | publisher=MTV | date=2008-11-12 | accessdate=2009-01-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219005322/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1599140/20081111/story.jhtml | archive-date=2008-12-19 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影的[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]於2009年3月21日在選定的地點發行，但已於2009年5月5日在其他零售商處更廣泛地銷售<ref>{{cite news| title=Twilight Blu-ray Mystery Solved| url=http://www.thehdroom.com/news/Twilight_Blu-ray_Mystery_Solved/4213| author=HD Room| publisher=[[The_HD_Room|The HD Room]]| date=2009-02-02| accessdate=2009-02-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208195137/http://thehdroom.com/news/Twilight_Blu-ray_Mystery_Solved/4213| archive-date=2010-02-08| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。截至2012年7月，電影已售出11,242,519張，收入達$201,190,019美元<ref>{{cite web |title=Twilight - DVD Sales |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2008/TWLIT-DVD.php |work=The Numbers |publisher=Nash Information Services |accessdate=2012-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408091659/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2008/TWLIT-DVD.php |archive-date=2009-04-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

